平台要成功有<span style=\"color: blue;\">影響力</span>，必須要有<span style=\"color: red;\">幾萬人、幾十萬人、幾百萬人</span>！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">C. 點解一定要起平台？</span><br />\n無論係選區議會、立法會、全港既領袖，要爭取獨立調查、五大訴求、保粵語、抗監控、甚至係港獨，<span style=\"color: red;\">【真民主】</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">都係致勝關鍵</span>，【政府<span style=\"color: red;\">擺明唔俾，唔通就坐係度等？</span>】<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">D. 咁急做咩？</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">打緊仗</span>呀大佬！勇武拉一個少一個，熱門又無幾多個post對抗爭有大幫助，和理非開始失敗主義、麻木、唔知做咩好&hellip;&hellip;如果<span style=\"color: blue;\">唔做D新既野、有用既野，</span><span style=\"color: red;\">過左十一，仲捱到幾耐？</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Telegram入Group</span>: <a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/OPIwDhNgTimdhP5Rz7spuQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FOPIwDhNgTimdhP5Rz7spuQ&d=9iHhAbkmMxvvE1I2I23sbcF7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=4e0c372f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/OPIwDhNgTimdhP5Rz7spuQ</a>"},{"pid":"dfeb6a149cd891e5bbaa682abc3ef03e0f382f2b","tid":1574971,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T15:56:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"303230c802e19146eb5225bce75274cf322d3b0e","tid":1574971,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T15:59:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pvsTHEi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpvsTHEi.jpg&h=e8bfe3ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">宣佈 和你suck 4.0 9月22 星期日見<br />\n<br />\nsuck 4.0 將會基於 hkmap.live 行動  <br />\n麻煩力推呢個livemap <br />\n對各位日後行動都非常大幫助<br />\n<br />\n請各位必須係 9月22日當日12點30分留意channel / 連登 / IG 最新消息<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n連登post:<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1568754\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1568754</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n TG : <a href=\"https://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=9iHhAbkmMxvvE1I2